@startuml
!theme plain
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "APP" as APP
participant "Middleware" as MW
participant "Banco de Comercio" as BDC

title POST /bdc/alias-remove?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/alias-remove
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /alias-remove
BDC --> MW: alias eliminado / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

@enduml
